        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Sprinkle over both your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 18-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>sesame crusted chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1619775056138-x200.jpg",
