            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [450ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and reduce the heat to low</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and stir through your <strong>mango chutney</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-7 min or until the sauce has thickened to a curry-like consistency – this is your <strong>katsu sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
