            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the katsu sauce is thickening, combine the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lime[s]</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash the<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and add it to the bowl with the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> and the <strong>dressing </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1619776258101-x200.jpg",
