            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sesame crusted chicken is cooked, transfer to a clean board and slice it finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
