    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced sesame crusted chicken</strong> over the <strong>katsu sauce</strong>, with the <strong>edamame brown rice</strong> and <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
